Usage: all_connected [-help] <single_object_collection_or_object> [-leaf]

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
<single_object_collection_or_object>     # net, pin, or port for which to
                                         # return the collection of connected
                                         # objects (string, required)
-leaf                                    # Returns all instance pins connected
                                         # to the specified net (bool, optional)